Getting Started (2 lines)

    git clone git://github.com/lloydchang/oe-made-easy.git
    cd oe-made-easy && ./core-image-minimal

This cleanly builds core-image-minimal recipe from OpenEmbedded-Core for you :-)
Afterwards, you can browse the ./oe-core directory to build incrementally

